---
---

<section class="nix-section">
	<div class="section-content">
		<div class="section-logo">
			<img src="/logos/nix-logo.svg" alt="NixOS" width="64" height="64" />
		</div>
		<h2>Nix Systems Design</h2>
		<p class="section-description">
			Declarative, reproducible infrastructure and development environments. 
			Infrastructure as code that actually works—deploy with confidence.
		</p>
		<div class="capabilities">
			<div class="capability">
				<h3>NixOS Infrastructure</h3>
				<p>Fully declarative server and workstation deployments. Atomic upgrades, instant rollbacks, and identical environments across dev and prod.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="capability">
				<h3>Flakes & Packages</h3>
				<p>Custom package repositories, development shells with pinned dependencies, and reproducible build pipelines.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="capability">
				<h3>Remote Deployment</h3>
				<p>nixos-rebuild deploy, colmena, and disko for bare-metal provisioning. Automated system provisioning at scale.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.nix-section {
		padding: 4rem 0;
		border-top: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
	}

	.section-content {
		text-align: center;
	}

	.section-logo {
		width: 64px;
		height: 64px;
		margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
	}

	.section-logo img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: contain;
	}

	:root.dark .section-logo img {
		filter: brightness(1.2);
	}

	h2 {
		font-size: 2rem;
		margin: 0 0 1rem;
	}

	.section-description {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		max-width: 600px;
		margin: 0 auto 2rem;
	}

	.capabilities {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 1.5rem;
		text-align: left;
	}

	.capability {
		background: var(--bg-color);
		border: 1px solid rgb(var(--gray-light));
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.capability:hover {
		border-color: var(--accent);
		transform: translateY(-4px);
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
	}

	.capability h3 {
		font-size: 1.1rem;
		margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
	}

	.capability p {
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
		margin: 0;
		line-height: 1.5;
	}

	@media (max-width: 720px) {
		.capabilities {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
		}
	}
</style>
